msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:38
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ktouch; is a program for learning touch typing. It helps you learn to "
#| "type on a keyboard quickly and correctly. Every finger has it's place on "
#| "the keyboard with associated keys to press."
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning touch typing. It helps you learn to "
"type on a keyboard quickly and correctly. Every finger has it's place on the "
"keyboard with associated keys to press."
msgstr ""
"&ktouch; est un programme pour apprendre la dactylographie. Il vous apprend "
"à saisir sur un clavier rapidement et correctement. Chaque doigt a sa place "
"sur le clavier avec les touches associées sur lesquelles il faut appuyer."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ktouch; helps you learn to touch type by providing you with text to "
#| "train on, and adjusts to different levels depending on how good you are. "
#| "It can display which key to press next, and correct finger to use."
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; helps you learn to touch type by providing you with text to "
"train on, and adjusts to different levels depending on how good you are. It "
"can display which key to press next, and correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&ktouch; vous apprend à dactylographier en vous fournissant des textes pour "
"s'entraîner et adapte le niveau de difficulté selon la façon dont vous êtes "
"bon. Il peut afficher la prochaine touche sur laquelle if faudra appuyer et "
"corriger par le doigt à utiliser."

